{"tid":533330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：戴啟思擊敗林定國　當選大律師公會新主席 (23:42)","createTime":"2018-01-18T15:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T17:22:03.000Z","uid":60665,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7adeb5ae691de36099718b07ea9225d6268f92","tid":533330,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180118/s00001/1516290111915?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180118%2Fs00001%2F1516290111915%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=dh2tHYykOLYIPQPChNkXpdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ad9ae10a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180118%2Fs00001%2F1516290111915%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=9fe0fd63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180118/s00001/1516290111915?web_push=1</a><br />\n<br />\n主席一職罕有出現競爭的大律師公會，今晚舉行會員大會改選主席及5名執委席位。現場未公布正式結果，但多個消息向本報透露，有「人權大狀」之稱的前主席戴啟思，擊敗現任主席林定國，當選新主席，至於執委票數仍在點算中。<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：【一地兩檢】律師會發聲明　籲進一步澄清基本法依據<br />\n<br />\n另外，屬林定國名單的2名副主席和正副名譽秘書共4個職位，在沒有競爭下自動當選連任。<br />\n<br />\n今晚大會氣氛熱烈，公會早前已預料出席人數眾多，由以往在高等法院內場地舉行大會，改為租借中環和記大廈一層樓層舉行。據了解，今晚高峰時約有400人出席大會，部分會員因座位不足須站立，大會原定傍晚6時45分召開，亦因人多延遲半小時。<br />\n<br />\n公會會員可授權他人代為投票，但多名重量級法律界人物今晚均親身投票，包括公會前主席李柱銘、張健利、李志喜、余若薇、梁家傑、陳景生、高浩文和林孟達，以及星級資深大律師余若海、潘熙和清洪等。"},{"pid":"a52389be14cbd21d1b7ee1bdc0a2e749bfe80f29","tid":533330,"uid":51978,"like":4,"dislike":41,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"完了 又俾洋鬼子掌權"},{"pid":"54b92f99c4df27f59f13a9c6d6464826b68c7d41","tid":533330,"uid":21139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5520ae4f8963edf44ed6f9fdb742c4e002f6d91a","tid":533330,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其他位都係林定國既人<br />\n要表決都係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f8486eadb86ad4c6a5e0bbb75f0b6862e7b01b","tid":533330,"uid":42767,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"傳統上第二年會選返同一個人做主席, 今次打破呢個傳統間接證明好多大律師覺得林定國team人出唔夠聲"},{"pid":"abe9e87262504f39fe9738ea8bab96c8b016a884","tid":533330,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5520ae4f8963edf44ed6f9fdb742c4e002f6d91a","tid":533330,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其他位都係林定國既人<br />\n要表決都係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"如果執委係佢既人就可以反敗為勝"},{"pid":"2189a7dc5736eb73e9d13f9b90a23b5f9e63e468","tid":533330,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c660f25cc649e8eb9adc8ba0de170159f31d2c9","tid":533330,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48a4a3840bc95df1927e80cc1eac7f4a150d381","tid":533330,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"等正式結果公佈先唱小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0820e55f407883ed135e595f19275ca7411474e","tid":533330,"uid":15984,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:07:32.